Alapis Posts Net Loss for 2010 of 931.4 Million Euros

-- B y   E l e n i   C h r e p a
-- 
2011-03-31T12:57:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/alapis-posts-net-loss-for-2010-of-931-4-million-euros-correct-.html
(Corrects loss to 931.4 million euros, adds attribution to
e-mailed statement.)  Alapis SA posted a 2010 loss of
931.4 million euros compared with a year earlier profit of 52.9
million euros, according to an e-mailed statement from the
Athens-based company today.  Sales were 946.6 million euros compared with 1.2 billion
euros a year earlier.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eleni Chrepa in Athens at 
 echrepa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Petrakis at 
 mpetrakis@bloomberg.net  